    "body" : "<pre><code>import org.apache.commons.io.FileUtils;\n\nFileUtils.cleanDirectory(directory); \n</code></pre>\n\n<p>There is this method available in the same file. This will also recursively deletes all sub-folders and files under them.</p>\n\n<p>Docs: <a href=\"http://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-io/javadocs/api-2.5/org/apache/commons/io/FileUtils.html#cleanDirectory(java.io.File)\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>org.apache.commons.io.FileUtils.cleanDirectory</code></a></p>\n"
