      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "On the other hand, if nobody is the first to use the external library, then it&#39;s less likely that others will expect to find similar behavior in that external library, and less likely that they will look there... don&#39;t we have enough Not Invented Here out there? If the library is cohesive and easy to add to my project, then I almost always prefer to add the library."
