    "body" : "<p>Or to use this in Java 8:</p>\n\n<pre><code>try {\n  Files.newDirectoryStream( directory ).forEach( file -&gt; {\n    try { Files.delete( file ); }\n    catch ( IOException e ) { throw new UncheckedIOException(e); }\n  } );\n}\ncatch ( IOException e ) {\n  e.printStackTrace();\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>It's a pity the exception handling is so bulky, otherwise it would be a one-liner ...</p>\n"
