    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<h1>Java 8 Stream</h1>\n\n<p>This deletes only files from <strong>ABC</strong> (sub-directories are untouched):</p>\n\n<pre><code>Arrays.stream(new File(\"C:/test/ABC/\").listFiles()).forEach(File::delete);\n</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This deletes only files from <strong>ABC</strong> (and sub-directories):</p>\n\n<pre><code>Files.walk(Paths.get(\"C:/test/ABC/\"))\n                .filter(Files::isRegularFile)\n                .map(Path::toFile)\n                .forEach(File::delete);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>^ This version requires handling the IOException</p>\n"
