    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I think this will work (based on NonlinearFruit previous answer): </p>\n\n<pre><code>Files.walk(Paths.get(\"C:/test/ABC/\"))\n                .sorted(Comparator.reverseOrder())\n                .map(Path::toFile)\n                .filter(item -&gt; !item.getPath().equals(\"C:/test/ABC/\"))\n                .forEach(File::delete);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Cheers!</p>\n"
