    "body" : "<p>In java 8, simply use:</p>\n<pre><code>public void clearDirectory(Path directory){\n    if (Files.exists(directory)) {\n            Files.list(directory)\n                 .forEach(\n                         path -&gt; {\n                             try {\n                                 if (Files.isDirectory(path)) {\n                                     clearDirectory(path);\n                                 }\n                                 Files.delete(path);\n                             } catch (IOException e) {\n                                 // todo handle exception\n                             }\n                         }\n                 );\n        }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
